                                           allow client multiple connections to client

                             blocking:

                                           the thread is suspended untill the operation is complete

                                           you need many threads in order not to waste time/ handle multiple connections

                             non-blocking:

                                           server does not wait, complete request when possible

                                           you can use a single thread to handle multiple connections

                                           cost of connection is cheap

                                          

